"diterima melalui alias."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:293
msgid ""
"Optionally, select the :ref:`Tags <documents/tags>` to automatically apply "
"to the files created through the alias."
msgstr ""
"Secara opsional, pilih :ref:`Tags <documents/tags>` untuk diterapkan secara "
"otomatis pada file yang dibuat melalui alias."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:297
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:302
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:297
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Label"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:304
msgid ""
"Tags help organize and categorize files, making it easier to search and "
"filter them. To configure tags for files, go to :menuselection:`Documents --"
"> Configuration --> Tags`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new tag. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`Tag Name`, select a :guilabel:`Color`, and optionally add "
"a :guilabel:`Tooltip` that appears when hovering over the tag."
msgstr ""
"Tag membantu mengatur dan mengategorikan file, sehingga lebih mudah untuk "
"mencari dan memfilternya. Untuk mengonfigurasi tag untuk file, "
"buka :menuselection:`Dokumen --> Konfigurasi --> Tag`. Klik :guilabel:`Baru` "
"untuk membuat tag baru. Masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Tag`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Warna`, dan secara opsional tambahkan :guilabel:`Tooltip` "
"yang muncul saat mengarahkan kursor ke tag."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:309
msgid ""
"To add tags to a file, open the file, click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` "
"(:guilabel:`Info & Tags`) in the upper-right corner next to the view icons, "
"and then, in the details panel, select a tag from the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan tag ke file, buka file, klik :icon:`fa-info-circle` "
"(:guilabel:`Info & Tags`) di sudut kanan atas di sebelah ikon tampilan, lalu "
"di panel detail, pilih tag dari daftar dropdown."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:314
msgid ""
":ref:`Alias tags <documents/email-aliases>` can also be used to "
"automatically apply tags to files created through the alias."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Tag alias <documents/email-aliases>` juga dapat digunakan untuk secara "
"otomatis menerapkan tag ke file yang dibuat melalui alias."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:320
msgid "Share and access rights"
msgstr "Bagikan dan hak akses"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:323
msgid ""
"You can only share folders and files and edit their access rights if you "
"have editing rights."
msgstr ""
"Anda hanya dapat membagikan folder dan file serta mengedit hak aksesnya jika "
"Anda memiliki hak edit."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:325
msgid "Access rights can be set on:"
msgstr "Hak akses dapat diatur pada:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:327
msgid ""
"folders: Select the folder, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) "
"icon, and select :guilabel:`Share`."
msgstr ""
"folder: Pilih folder, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`roda gigi`), dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Bagikan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:329
msgid "files: Open the file and click :guilabel:`Share` in the top bar."
msgstr "file: Buka file dan klik :guilabel:`Bagikan` di bilah atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:331
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Share` pop-up, grant access to specific users or contacts "
"by selecting their name from the dropdown menu or by adding their email "
"address manually, then select :guilabel:`Viewer` or :guilabel:`Editor`."
msgstr ""
"Di pop-up :guilabel:`Share`, berikan akses kepada user atau kontak tertentu "
"dengan memilih nama mereka dari menu dropdown atau dengan menambahkan alamat "
"email mereka secara manual, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Viewer` "
"atau :guilabel:`Editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:336
msgid ""
"To remove a permission or set an expiration date for it, hover the mouse "
"over the relevant contact and click the :icon:`fa-remove` "
"(:guilabel:`remove`) or :icon:`fa-calendar` (:guilabel:`calendar`) button, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus izin atau menetapkan tanggal kedaluwarsa untuknya, arahkan "
"kursor ke kontak yang relevan dan klik tombol :icon:`fa-remove` "
"(:guilabel:`hapus`) atau :icon:`fa-calendar` (:guilabel:`kalender`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:0
msgid "Hover the mouse over a permission to reveal the buttons."
msgstr "Arahkan kursor ke izin untuk menampilkan tombol."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:343
msgid ""
"To set :guilabel:`General access` for :guilabel:`Internal users` "
"or :guilabel:`Anyone with the link`, "
"select :guilabel:`Viewer`, :guilabel:`Editor`, or :guilabel:`None` (to "
"restrict access completely). For :guilabel:`Anyone with the link`, you can "
"further specify whether the folder or file should "
"be :guilabel:`Discoverable` (accessible through browsing) or require that "
"users :guilabel:`Must have the link to access` it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur :guilabel:`General access` untuk :guilabel:`Internal users` "
"atau :guilabel:`Anyone with the link`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Viewer`, :guilabel:`Editor`, atau :guilabel:`None` (untuk "
"membatasi akses sepenuhnya). Untuk :guilabel:`Anyone with the link`, Anda "
"dapat menentukan lebih lanjut apakah folder atau file "
"harus :guilabel:`Discoverable` (dapat diakses melalui penjelajahan) atau "
"mengharuskan user untuk :guilabel:`Must have the link to access`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:350
msgid ""
"Public users :guilabel:`Must have the link to access` a folder or file on "
"the portal when connecting for the first time."
msgstr ""
"User publik :guilabel:`Must have the link to access` folder atau file di "
"portal saat terhubung untuk pertama kalinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:352
msgid ""
"Each folder and file URL includes the access rights that have been set for "
"it. When you share a folder, the person you share it with is directed to a "
"dedicated portal where they can view the files in that folder, excluding any "
"with restricted access."
msgstr ""
"Setiap URL folder dan file menyertakan hak akses yang telah diatur untuknya. "
"Saat Anda membagikan folder, orang yang Anda bagikan akan diarahkan ke "
"portal khusus tempat mereka dapat melihat file di folder tersebut, tidak "
"termasuk file dengan akses terbatas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:357
msgid ""
":doc:`Portal users </applications/general/users/portal>` can access folders "
"and files they have permission to view or edit through the customer portal "
"by clicking the :guilabel:`Documents` card."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Portal users </applications/general/users/portal>` dapat mengakses "
"folder dan file yang mereka izinkan untuk dilihat atau diedit melalui portal "
"pelanggan dengan mengklik kartu :guilabel:`Documents`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:364
msgid "File digitization with AI"
msgstr "Digitalisasi file dengan AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:366
msgid ""
"Files available in the Finance folder can be digitized. Select the file, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Vendor Bill`, :guilabel:`Create Customer Invoice`, "
"or :guilabel:`Create Customer Credit Note`, then click :guilabel:`Send for "
"Digitization`."
msgstr ""
"File yang tersedia di folder Keuangan dapat didigitalkan. Pilih file, "
"klik :guilabel:`Buat Tagihan Vendor`, :guilabel:`Buat Faktur Pelanggan`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Buat Nota Kredit Pelanggan`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Kirim "
"untuk Digitalisasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:371
msgid ""
":doc:`AI-powered document digitization <../finance/accounting/vendor_bills/"
"invoice_digitization>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Digitalisasi dokumen bertenaga AI <../finance/accounting/vendor_bills/"
"invoice_digitization>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:3
msgid "Knowledge"
msgstr "Pengetahuan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Odoo Knowledge** is a multipurpose productivity app that allows internal "
"users to enrich their business knowledge base by providing information "
"gathered individually or collaboratively."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Pengetahuan** adalah aplikasi produktivitas multiguna yang "
"memungkinkan pengguna internal untuk memperkaya basis pengetahuan bisnis "
"mereka dengan menyediakan informasi yang dikumpulkan secara individual atau "
"kolaboratif."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:8
msgid ""
"The pages on which they gather content are called *articles*. They are "
"mainly composed of a title and a body. The latter is an HTML field "
"containing text, images, links, records from other models, templates, etc."
msgstr ""
"Halaman tempat mereka mengumpulkan konten disebut *artikel*. Artikel "
"tersebut terutama terdiri dari judul dan isi. Yang terakhir adalah kolom "
"HTML yang berisi teks, gambar, tautan, rekaman dari model lain, template, "
"dll."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:13
msgid "`Knowledge product page <https://www.odoo.com/app/knowledge>`_"
msgstr "`Halaman produk Pengetahuan <https://www.odoo.com/app/knowledge>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:18
msgid "Article creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan artikel"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:20
msgid ""
"Knowledge articles can be created from scratch or a pre-configured template. "
"When an article is created under another, the original one is the **parent "
"article**, while the new one is called a **child** or **nested article**, "
"indicating its subordinate position. This structure helps organize content "
"by establishing clear relationships between related articles."
msgstr ""
"Artikel Pengetahuan dapat dibuat dari awal atau template yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya. Ketika artikel dibuat di bawah artikel lain, "
"artikel asli adalah **artikel induk**, sedangkan artikel baru disebut "
"**artikel anak** atau **artikel bersarang**, menunjukkan posisi bawahannya. "
"Struktur ini membantu mengatur konten dengan membuat hubungan yang jelas "
"antara artikel-artikel terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create a nested article, hover over an article in the sidebar tree and "
"click the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat artikel bersarang, arahkan kursor ke artikel di pohon bilah "
