"elektronik yang aman, efisien, dan patuh secara hukum di Angola."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/angola.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for electronic signatures in Angola"
msgstr "Kerangka hukum untuk tanda tangan elektronik di Angola"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/angola.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Angola, electronic signatures are regulated under the Presidential Decree "
"312/2018 and Executive Order 74/2019. The law establishes the legal basis "
"for acknowledging electronic records, contracts, and digital signatures. The "
"key points of the law include:"
msgstr ""
"Di Angola, tanda tangan elektronik diatur berdasarkan Keputusan Presiden "
"312/2018 dan Perintah Eksekutif 74/2019. Undang-undang ini menetapkan dasar "
"hukum untuk mengakui catatan elektronik, kontrak, dan tanda tangan digital. "
"Poin-poin utama undang-undang ini meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/angola.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Certified electronic signature**: digital signature generated using a "
"digital certificate supplied by a qualified provider. In some cases, only "
"the certified electronic signature has legal and juridical validity in "
"Angola. In those cases, simple electronic signatures like the Odoo Signature "
"only work as a proof of the agreement to celebrate the corresponding "
"transaction, which will be submitted to the authority's criteria."
msgstr ""
"**Tanda tangan elektronik tersertifikasi**: tanda tangan digital yang "
"dihasilkan menggunakan sertifikat digital yang disediakan oleh penyedia "
"berkualifikasi. Dalam beberapa kasus, hanya tanda tangan elektronik "
"tersertifikasi yang memiliki validitas hukum dan yuridis di Angola. Dalam "
"kasus tersebut, tanda tangan elektronik sederhana seperti Odoo Sign hanya "
"berfungsi sebagai bukti kesepakatan untuk melakukan transaksi terkait, yang "
"akan diserahkan kepada kriteria otoritas."

