":ref:`mengonversinya menjadi tabel pivot dinamis <spreadsheet/dynamic-pivot-"
"tables/create>` untuk dapat memanipulasi dimensi dan measures"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:484
msgid ""
":ref:`duplicate the pivot table <spreadsheet/insert/pivot-table-duplicate>` "
