#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:492
msgid "Duplicate a pivot table"
msgstr "Duplikasi tabel pivot"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:494
msgid ""
"Duplicating a pivot table via the pivot table's properties creates an "
"additional data source. This allows for different manipulations to be "
"performed on the same data within one spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Menduplikasi tabel pivot melalui properti tabel pivot akan membuat sumber "
"data tambahan. Ini memungkinkan manipulasi yang berbeda dilakukan pada data "
"yang sama dalam satu spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:497
msgid ""
"For example, you can see the same data aggregated by different dimensions or "
"use :doc:`global filters <work_with_data/global_filters>` to offset the date "
"and create pivot tables that compare the current period's data with a "
"previous period."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, Anda dapat melihat data yang sama diagregasikan berdasarkan "
"dimensi yang berbeda atau menggunakan :doc:`filter global <work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` untuk mengimbangi tanggal dan membuat tabel pivot yang "
"membandingkan data periode saat ini dengan periode sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:501
msgid "To duplicate a pivot table, perform the following steps:"
msgstr "Untuk menduplikasi tabel pivot, lakukan langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:503
msgid ""
"With the :ref:`pivot table properties <spreadsheet/insert/pivot-table-"
"properties>` open, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"then :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplicate`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan :ref:`properti tabel pivot <spreadsheet/insert/pivot-table-"
"properties>` terbuka, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` "
"kemudian :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplicate`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:506
msgid ""
"The duplicated pivot table is automatically inserted into a new sheet in the "
"spreadsheet, with the pivot table properties open in the right pane."
msgstr ""
"Tabel pivot yang diduplikasi secara otomatis disisipkan ke dalam sheet baru "
"di spreadsheet, dengan properti tabel pivot terbuka di panel kanan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:508
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Name` in the properties pane and the sheet tab if needed."
msgstr "Edit :guilabel:`Name` di panel properti dan tab sheet jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:510
msgid ""
"The new data source is assigned the next available pivot table ID. For "
"example, if no other pivot tables have been inserted in the meantime, "
"duplicating *Pivot #1* results in the creation of *Pivot #2*."
msgstr ""
"Sumber data baru diberikan ID tabel pivot berikutnya yang tersedia. "
"Misalnya, jika tidak ada tabel pivot lain yang telah disisipkan sementara "
"itu, menduplikasi *Pivot #1* menghasilkan pembuatan *Pivot #2*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:515
msgid ""
"Duplicating an inserted pivot table by copying and pasting it or by "
"duplicating the sheet does not create a new data source. Any changes made to "
"the pivot table's properties would therefore impact any copies of the pivot "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Menduplikasi tabel pivot yang telah disisipkan dengan menyalin dan "
"menempelkannya atau dengan menduplikasi sheet tidak membuat sumber data "
"baru. Oleh karena itu, perubahan apa pun yang dibuat pada properti tabel "
"pivot akan memengaruhi salinan tabel pivot tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:518
msgid ""
"When a pivot table is duplicated, the new pivot table is by default "
"a :doc:`dynamic pivot table <work_with_data/dynamic_pivot_tables>`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tabel pivot diduplikasi, tabel pivot baru secara default "
"adalah :doc:`tabel pivot dinamis <work_with_data/dynamic_pivot_tables>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:524
msgid "Delete a pivot table"
msgstr "Menghapus tabel pivot"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:526
msgid ""
"To fully delete a pivot table and the underlying data source from a "
"spreadsheet, perform the following steps in any order:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk sepenuhnya menghapus tabel pivot dan sumber data yang mendasarinya "
"dari spreadsheet, lakukan langkah-langkah berikut dalam urutan apa pun:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:531
msgid ""
"From the :ref:`properties pane <spreadsheet/insert/pivot-table-properties>` "
"of the relevant pivot table, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` "
"icon then :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete`. This deletes the data source "
"of the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Dari :ref:`panel properti <spreadsheet/insert/pivot-table-properties>` tabel "
"pivot yang relevan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` "
"kemudian :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete`. Ini akan menghapus sumber data "
"dari tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:538
msgid "Insert a chart"
msgstr "Menyisipkan grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:540
msgid "To insert a chart from an Odoo database into an Odoo spreadsheet:"
msgstr "Untuk menyisipkan grafik dari database Odoo ke dalam spreadsheet Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:542
msgid ""
"With the relevant graph view open in your database, click :guilabel:`Insert "
"in Spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan tampilan grafik yang relevan terbuka di database Anda, "
"klik :guilabel:`Sisipkan di Spreadsheet`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:543
msgid ""
"In the window that opens, edit the :guilabel:`Name of the graph` if needed."
msgstr "Di jendela yang terbuka, edit :guilabel:`Nama grafik` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:545
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Blank spreadsheet` or select in which existing spreadsheet "
"the chart should be inserted."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Blank spreadsheet` atau pilih spreadsheet yang sudah ada di "
"mana chart akan disisipkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:556
msgid ""
"Charts are inserted on the first sheet of the spreadsheet. A pane on the "
"right side of the screen shows the :ref:`chart properties <spreadsheet/"
"visualize/chart-properties>`, where various aspects of the chart's "
"configuration and design can be modified."
msgstr ""
"Bagan disisipkan pada sheet pertama spreadsheet. Panel di sisi kanan layar "
"menampilkan :ref:`properti bagan <spreadsheet/visualize/chart-properties>`, "
"di mana berbagai aspek konfigurasi dan desain bagan dapat dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:561
msgid ""
"Clicking on a data point in a chart opens the relevant list view in the "
"database. In the example, clicking on :guilabel:`Jessica Childs` opens the "
"list view of all sales by this salesperson that match the domain of the "
"chart."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik titik data dalam grafik akan membuka tampilan daftar yang relevan "
"di database. Dalam contoh ini, mengklik :guilabel:`Jessica Childs` akan "
"membuka tampilan daftar semua penjualan oleh tenaga penjual ini yang sesuai "
"dengan domain grafik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:0
msgid "A clickable link to an Odoo menu plus clickable data point"
msgstr ""
"Tautan yang dapat diklik ke menu Odoo plus titik data yang dapat diklik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:571
msgid "Insert clickable links"
msgstr "Sisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:573
msgid ""
"Adding links to related or supporting information can make your report or "
"dashboard more user-friendly and effective."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan tautan ke informasi terkait atau pendukung dapat membuat laporan "
"atau dashboard Anda lebih ramah pengguna dan efektif."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:576
msgid ""
"You can :ref:`insert a clickable link from any spreadsheet cell <spreadsheet/"
"insert/clickable-links-cell>` to:"
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat :ref:`menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari sel spreadsheet "
"mana pun <spreadsheet/insert/clickable-links-cell>` ke:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:579
msgid "an Odoo menu item"
msgstr "item menu Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:580
msgid "another sheet inside the same spreadsheet"
msgstr "sheet lain di dalam spreadsheet yang sama"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:581
msgid "an external URL"
msgstr "URL eksternal"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:584
msgid ""
"Clicking a link to a menu item provides the same result as navigating via "
"the Odoo menu within an app, e.g., the menu item :guilabel:`Sales/Orders/"
"Quotations` corresponds to the default view when navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Sales --> Orders --> Quotations`."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik tautan ke item menu memberikan hasil yang sama dengan menavigasi "
"melalui menu Odoo dalam aplikasi, misalnya, item menu :guilabel:`Penjualan/"
"Pesanan/Penawaran` sesuai dengan tampilan default saat menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Penjualan --> Pesanan --> Penawaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:587
msgid ""
"It is also possible to insert a clickable link to a specific view of a model "
"in a spreadsheet starting from the view itself. However, as this method "
"inserts each new link in a new sheet, it is more efficient to create links "
"to specific views starting from the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik ke tampilan "
"spesifik dari sebuah model dalam spreadsheet dimulai dari tampilan itu "
"sendiri. Namun, karena metode ini menyisipkan setiap tautan baru dalam sheet "
"baru, lebih efisien untuk membuat tautan ke tampilan spesifik dimulai dari "
"spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:591
msgid ""
"You can :ref:`insert a clickable link from any chart <spreadsheet/insert/"
"clickable-links-chart>` to an Odoo menu item."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat :ref:`menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari grafik mana pun "
"<spreadsheet/insert/clickable-links-chart>` ke item menu Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:597
msgid "Insert a clickable link from a cell"
msgstr "Menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari sel"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:599
msgid "To insert a clickable link from a cell:"
msgstr "Untuk menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari sel:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:601
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Insert -->` :icon:`fa-link` :menuselection:`Link` from "
"the menu bar or right-click on the cell, then click :icon:`fa-"
"link` :guilabel:`Insert link`. Next, depending on the desired outcome, "
"perform one of the following actions:"
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Insert -->` :icon:`fa-link` :menuselection:`Link` dari "
"menu bar atau klik kanan pada sel, kemudian klik :icon:`fa-"
"link` :guilabel:`Insert link`. Selanjutnya, tergantung pada hasil yang "
"diinginkan, lakukan salah satu tindakan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:605
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon, then :guilabel:`Link an "
"Odoo menu`. Select the relevant menu item from the list or "
"click :guilabel:`Search more` to choose from a list of all menu items. "
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)`, kemudian :guilabel:`Link an "
"Odoo menu`. Pilih item menu yang relevan dari daftar atau "
"klik :guilabel:`Search more` untuk memilih dari daftar semua item menu. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:608
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon, then :guilabel:`Link "
"sheet`, then choose the relevant sheet from the current spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)`, kemudian :guilabel:`Link "
"sheet`, lalu pilih sheet yang relevan dari spreadsheet saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:610
msgid "Under :guilabel:`Link`, type a URL."
msgstr "Di bawah :guilabel:`Link`, ketik URL."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:612
msgid "Enter or edit the label for the link in the :guilabel:`Text` field."
msgstr "Masukkan atau edit label untuk tautan di kolom :guilabel:`Text`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:618
msgid "Insert a clickable link from a chart"
msgstr "Menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:620
msgid "To insert a clickable link from a chart to an Odoo menu item:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyisipkan tautan yang dapat diklik dari grafik ke item menu Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:622
msgid ""
"Hover over the top right of the chart's box, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon, then :icon:`fa-pencil-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Edit`. The chart properties appear at the right of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Arahkan kursor ke kanan atas kotak grafik, kemudian klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(menu)`, kemudian :icon:`fa-pencil-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Edit`. Properti grafik muncul di sebelah kanan layar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:625
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the :icon:`fa-sliders` :guilabel:`Configuration` tab of the "
"chart properties pane, click under :guilabel:`Link to Odoo menu`, then "
"select a menu."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian bawah tab :icon:`fa-sliders` :guilabel:`Konfigurasi` dari panel "
"properti grafik, klik di bawah :guilabel:`Tautan ke menu Odoo`, lalu pilih "
"menu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:628
msgid ""
"Hover over the top right of the chart's box to see that a new :icon:`fa-"
"external-link` :guilabel:`(external link)` icon has been added."
msgstr ""
"Arahkan kursor ke kanan atas kotak grafik untuk melihat bahwa ikon :icon:`fa-"
"external-link` :guilabel:`(external link)` baru telah ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:634
msgid "Insert financial data"
msgstr "Menyisipkan data finansial"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:636
msgid ""
"When building reports and dashboards, it may be useful to include certain "
"accounting-related data, such as account IDs, credits and debits for "
"specific accounts, and dates of the start and end of the tax year."
msgstr ""
"Ketika membangun laporan dan dashboard, mungkin berguna untuk menyertakan "
"data terkait akuntansi tertentu, seperti ID akun, kredit dan debit untuk "
"akun tertentu, dan tanggal awal dan akhir tahun pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert.rst:640
msgid ""
":ref:`Odoo-specific spreadsheet functions <spreadsheet/functions/odoo>` "
"allow you to retrieve such accounting data from your database and insert it "
"into a spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Fungsi spreadsheet khusus Odoo <spreadsheet/functions/odoo>` "
"memungkinkan Anda mengambil data akuntansi tersebut dari database Anda dan "
"menyisipkannya ke dalam spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:3
msgid "Share and collaborate"
msgstr "Bagikan dan berkolaborasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo Spreadsheet offers various features that allow for efficient real-time "
"collaboration while ensuring the appropriate level of control and "
"traceability, including:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Spreadsheet menawarkan berbagai fitur yang memungkinkan kolaborasi real-"
"time yang efisien sambil memastikan tingkat kontrol dan ketertelusuran yang "
"sesuai, termasuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:8
msgid ""
":ref:`permission-based sharing <spreadsheet/collaboration/access-sharing>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`pembagian berbasis izin <spreadsheet/collaboration/access-sharing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`version history <spreadsheet/get-started/manage-spreadsheets-"
"versioning>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`riwayat versi <spreadsheet/get-started/manage-spreadsheets-versioning>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:10
msgid ""
"discussions via :ref:`comments and the spreadsheet's chatter thread "
"<spreadsheet/collaboration/chatter>`"
msgstr ""
"diskusi melalui :ref:`komentar dan thread chatter spreadsheet <spreadsheet/"
"collaboration/chatter>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:16
msgid "Access and sharing"
msgstr "Akses dan pembagian"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:18
msgid ""
"In principle, the rights to access Odoo spreadsheets are handled "
"like :ref:`any other file in the Documents app <documents/access-"
"rights>`. :ref:`Roles and permissions <spreadsheet/collaboration/roles-"
"permissions>` are either inherited from the folder a spreadsheet is saved in "
"or controlled at the level of the spreadsheet itself."
msgstr ""
"Pada prinsipnya, hak untuk mengakses spreadsheet Odoo ditangani "
"seperti :ref:`file lain di aplikasi Dokumen <documents/access-"
"rights>`. :ref:`Peran dan izin <spreadsheet/collaboration/roles-"
"permissions>` baik diwarisi dari folder tempat spreadsheet disimpan atau "
"dikontrol di tingkat spreadsheet itu sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:23
msgid ""
"However, there are important differences to consider "
"between :ref:`spreadsheets that contain only static data <spreadsheet/"
"collaboration/static-spreadsheet>` and :ref:`spreadsheets that contain "
"dynamic Odoo data <spreadsheet/collaboration/dynamic-spreadsheet>`, in terms "
"of both access and data visibility."
msgstr ""
"Namun, ada perbedaan penting yang perlu dipertimbangkan "
"antara :ref:`spreadsheet yang hanya berisi data statis <spreadsheet/"
"collaboration/static-spreadsheet>` dan :ref:`spreadsheet yang berisi data "
"dinamis Odoo <spreadsheet/collaboration/dynamic-spreadsheet>`, baik dalam "
"hal akses maupun visibilitas data."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:30
msgid ""
"Access to a folder or spreadsheet can be managed by its owner or any user "
"with :guilabel:`Editor` rights."
msgstr ""
"Akses ke folder atau spreadsheet dapat dikelola oleh pemiliknya atau user "
"mana pun dengan hak :guilabel:`Editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:32
msgid ""
"A user with :guilabel:`Viewer` rights cannot share a spreadsheet with a "
"specific user directly, but can copy a link to the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"User dengan hak :guilabel:`Viewer` tidak dapat membagikan spreadsheet dengan "
"user tertentu secara langsung, tetapi dapat menyalin link ke spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:34
msgid ""
"Any user with access to a spreadsheet can download it as an `.xlsx` file by "
"clicking :menuselection:`File -->` :icon:`os-"
"download` :menuselection:`Download`  from the menu bar. If the spreadsheet "
"contained dynamic data, the values are frozen at the moment of download."
msgstr ""
"User mana pun yang memiliki akses ke spreadsheet dapat mengunduhnya sebagai "
"file `.xlsx` dengan mengklik :menuselection:`File -->` :icon:`os-"
"download` :menuselection:`Download` dari menu bar. Jika spreadsheet berisi "
"data dinamis, nilainya dibekukan pada saat pengunduhan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:41
msgid "Roles and permissions"
msgstr "Peran dan izin"

