#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/axivox_config.rst:None
msgid "Integration of Axivox user in the Odoo user preference."
msgstr "Integrasi user Axivox di preferensi user Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/axivox_config.rst:63
msgid ""
"Access the domain on the Axivox administrative panel by navigating to "
"`https://manage.axivox.com/ <https://manage.axivox.com/>`_. After logging "
"into the portal, go to :menuselection:`Users --> Edit (next to the user) --> "
"SIP Identifiers tab --> SIP username / SIP password`."
msgstr ""
"Akses domain di panel administratif Axivox dengan membuka `https://"
"manage.axivox.com/ <https://manage.axivox.com/>`_. Setelah masuk ke portal, "
"buka :menuselection:`Users --> Edit (di samping user) --> tab SIP "
"Identifiers --> SIP username / SIP password`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/axivox_config.rst:0
msgid "SIP credentials in the Axivox manager."
msgstr "Kredensial SIP di pengelola Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/axivox_config.rst:72
msgid ""
"When entering the :guilabel:`SIP Password` into the "
"user's :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, this value **must** be typed out "
"manually and **not** pasted in. Pasting in causes a `401 server rejection "
"error`."
msgstr ""
"Saat memasukkan :guilabel:`SIP Password` ke tab :guilabel:`Preferences` "
"user, nilai ini **harus** diketik secara manual dan **tidak** ditempelkan. "
"Menempelkan menyebabkan `kesalahan penolakan server 401`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:3
msgid "Call queues"
msgstr "Antrian panggilan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:5
msgid ""
"A call queue organizes and routes incoming calls when all agents are busy, "
"placing callers on hold in the order they called. This system helps manage "
"high call volumes more efficiently, ensures fair workload distribution, and "
"provides a more predictable experience for both callers and agents."
msgstr ""
"Antrean panggilan mengatur dan mengarahkan panggilan masuk ketika semua agen "
"sibuk, menempatkan penelepon dalam mode tahan sesuai urutan mereka "
"menelepon. Sistem ini membantu mengelola volume panggilan tinggi dengan "
"lebih efisien, memastikan distribusi beban kerja yang adil, dan memberikan "
"pengalaman yang lebih dapat diprediksi bagi penelepon maupun agen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:9
msgid ""
"This document explains how to configure call queue settings and log into a "
"queue from the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini menjelaskan cara mengonfigurasi pengaturan antrean panggilan dan "
"masuk ke antrean dari database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:13
msgid ":ref:`Set up on hold music <voip/axivox/music_on_hold>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Atur musik saat ditahan <voip/axivox/music_on_hold>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:16
msgid "Add a queue"
msgstr "Tambahkan antrean"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:18
msgid ""
"To add a call queue in Axivox, navigate to the `Axivox management console "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. In the left menu, click :guilabel:`Queues`. "
"Next, click :guilabel:`Add a queue`. From here, set up the call queue."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan antrean panggilan di Axivox, buka `konsol manajemen Axivox "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Di menu sebelah kiri, "
"klik :guilabel:`Queues`. Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Add a queue`. Dari "
"sini, atur antrean panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:22
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: The call queue's name. A required field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name`: Nama antrean panggilan. Kolom wajib diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:23
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Internal Extension`: The extension agents can transfer callers "
"to. A required field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Internal Extension`: Extension yang dapat digunakan agen untuk "
"mentransfer penelepon. Kolom wajib diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:24
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Strategy`: How calls are routed. Choose the option that best "
"matches the company's needs for this call queue:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Strategy`: Cara panggilan diarahkan. Pilih opsi yang paling "
"sesuai dengan kebutuhan perusahaan untuk antrean panggilan ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:27
msgid ":guilabel:`Call all available agents`: The call is sent to every agent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Call all available agents`: Panggilan dikirim ke setiap agen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Calls the agent who has received the call for the longest time`: "
"The call is sent to the agent with the longest idle time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Calls the agent who has received the call for the longest time`: "
"Panggilan dikirim ke agen dengan waktu idle terlama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Calls the agent who has received the least call`: The call is "
"sent to the agent who has handled the fewest calls in a time window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Calls the agent who has received the least call`: Panggilan "
"dikirim ke agen yang telah menangani panggilan paling sedikit dalam jangka "
"waktu tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:32
msgid ":guilabel:`Call a random agent`: The call is sent to a random agent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Call a random agent`: Panggilan dikirim ke agen secara acak."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Call agents one after the other`: The call is sent to the next "
"agent in a specified order. This order is remembered, and the order does not "
"reset after each call."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Panggil agen satu per satu`: Panggilan dikirim ke agen berikutnya "
"dalam urutan yang ditentukan. Urutan ini diingat, dan urutan tidak diatur "
"ulang setelah setiap panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Call agents one after the other starting with the first in the "
"list`: The call is sent to the next agent in a specified order. This order "
"is remembered, and the order does reset after each call."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Panggil agen satu per satu dimulai dari yang pertama dalam "
"daftar`: Panggilan dikirim ke agen berikutnya dalam urutan yang ditentukan. "
"Urutan ini diingat, dan urutan diatur ulang setelah setiap panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Maximum waiting time in seconds`: How long a customer can wait in "
"the queue before getting forwarded to voicemail or a specific agent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Waktu tunggu maksimum dalam detik`: Berapa lama pelanggan dapat "
"menunggu dalam antrian sebelum diteruskan ke pesan suara atau agen tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Maximum duration of ringing at an agent`: How long an individual "
"agent's phone rings before the call gets moved onto the next step in the "
"dial plan. Learn more about :doc:`dial plans <dial_plan_basics>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Durasi maksimum dering pada agen`: Berapa lama telepon agen "
"individu berdering sebelum panggilan dipindahkan ke langkah berikutnya dalam "
"rencana panggilan. Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang :doc:`rencana panggilan "
"<dial_plan_basics>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Static agents`: Agents in the queue who receive calls without "
"logging in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Agen statis`: Agen dalam antrian yang menerima panggilan tanpa "
"masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dynamic agents`: Agents who must log into the queue to receive "
"calls from it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Agen dinamis`: Agen yang harus masuk ke antrian untuk menerima "
"panggilan darinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:48
msgid ":ref:`voip/axivox/music_on_hold`"
msgstr ":ref:`voip/axivox/music_on_hold`"

