#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:164
msgid "Linphone"
msgstr "Linphone"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:166
msgid ""
"*Linphone* is an open-source :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet "
"Protocol)` :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` softphone, used for "
"voice, video, messaging (group and individual), as well as conference calls."
msgstr ""
"*Linphone* adalah softphone :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet "
"Protocol)` :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` sumber terbuka yang "
"digunakan untuk suara, video, perpesanan (grup dan individual), serta "
"panggilan konferensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:170
msgid ""
"To start using the *Linphone* app, download it to the device, via the "
"`Linphone download page <https://new.linphone.org/technical-corner/linphone?"
"qt-technical_corner=2#qt-technical_corner>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mulai menggunakan aplikasi *Linphone*, unduh ke perangkat melalui "
"`halaman unduhan Linphone <https://new.linphone.org/technical-corner/"
"linphone?qt-technical_corner=2#qt-technical_corner>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:173
msgid ""
"A mobile device is the most common installation, and this document covers "
"how to set up the *Linphone* IOS application. Screenshots and steps may "
"differ depending on the circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat seluler adalah instalasi yang paling umum, dan dokumen ini "
"menjelaskan cara menyiapkan aplikasi *Linphone* IOS. Tangkapan layar dan "
"langkah-langkah mungkin berbeda tergantung pada keadaan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:176
msgid ""
"To begin configuring *Linphone* for use with a :abbr:`SIP (Session "
"Initiation Protocol)` provider, first open *Linphone*, and an assistant "
"screen appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mulai mengonfigurasi *Linphone* untuk digunakan dengan "
"penyedia :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)`, pertama buka *Linphone*, "
"dan layar asisten muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:179
msgid ""
"From this screen, select :guilabel:`Use SIP Account`. Then, on the following "
"screen, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Username`, :guilabel:`Password`, :guilabel:`Domain`, "
"and :guilabel:`Display Name`. Once complete, press :guilabel:`Login`."
msgstr ""
"Dari layar ini, pilih :guilabel:`Use SIP Account`. Kemudian, pada layar "
"berikutnya, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Username`, :guilabel:`Password`, :guilabel:`Domain`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Display Name`. Setelah selesai, tekan :guilabel:`Login`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:183
msgid ""
"At this point, *Linphone* is ready to start making calls, once there is a "
"green button at the top of the application screen that "
"reads, :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ""
"Pada titik ini, *Linphone* siap untuk mulai melakukan panggilan setelah ada "
"tombol hijau di bagian atas layar aplikasi yang "
"bertuliskan :guilabel:`Connected`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:None
msgid "Linphone account setup, registration successful."
msgstr "Pengaturan akun Linphone, pendaftaran berhasil."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:191
msgid ""
"*Linphone* makes a variety of applications for mobile and desktop devices in "
"operating systems, such as Windows, Linux, Apple, and Android. Because "
"*Linphone* is an open-source project, many new updates are released on a "
"regular basis."
msgstr ""
"*Linphone* menyediakan berbagai aplikasi untuk perangkat seluler dan desktop "
"dalam sistem operasi seperti Windows, Linux, Apple, dan Android. Karena "
"*Linphone* adalah proyek sumber terbuka, banyak pembaruan baru dirilis "
"secara berkala."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:195
msgid ""
"See `Linphone's wiki-documentation page <https://wiki.linphone.org/xwiki/"
"wiki/public/view/Linphone/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Lihat `halaman dokumentasi wiki Linphone <https://wiki.linphone.org/xwiki/"
"wiki/public/view/Linphone/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:3
msgid "VoIP services in Odoo with DIDWW"
msgstr "Layanan VoIP di Odoo dengan DIDWW"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:5
msgid ""
"*DIDWW* is a global *VoIP* and SIP trunking provider. An active account with "
"DIDWW is required to use this service."
msgstr ""
"*DIDWW* adalah penyedia *VoIP* dan SIP trunking global. Akun aktif dengan "
"DIDWW diperlukan untuk menggunakan layanan ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:8
msgid ""
"Before creating an account with DIDWW, make sure that the company's location "
"and the applicable regions are supported by DIDWW's services."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum membuat akun dengan DIDWW, pastikan bahwa lokasi perusahaan dan "
"wilayah yang berlaku didukung oleh layanan DIDWW."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:12
msgid "DIDWW setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan DIDWW"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:14
msgid ""
"After verifying country coverage and availability, create an account with "
"`DIDWW <https://www.didww.com/>`_. Then navigate to the `DIDWW Dashboard "
"<https://my.didww.com/#/dashboard>`_."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memverifikasi cakupan dan ketersediaan negara, buat akun dengan "
"`DIDWW <https://www.didww.com/>`_. Kemudian navigasikan ke `DIDWW Dashboard "
"<https://my.didww.com/#/dashboard>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:18
msgid ""
"To transfer existing numbers from an existing telephone network service "
"provider, follow the steps outlined on the `DIDWW website <https://"
"doc.didww.com/phone-numbers/number-porting/index.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mentransfer nomor yang ada dari penyedia layanan jaringan telepon yang "
"ada, ikuti langkah-langkah yang diuraikan di `website DIDWW <https://"
"doc.didww.com/phone-numbers/number-porting/index.html>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:22
msgid "Purchase new numbers"
msgstr "Beli nomor baru"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:24
msgid ""
"To puchase new phone numbers, click :guilabel:`Buy Numbers` in the "
"dashboard, then follow the instructions to complete the purchase."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membeli nomor telepon baru, klik :guilabel:`Buy Numbers` di dashboard, "
"kemudian ikuti instruksi untuk menyelesaikan pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:27
msgid ""
"When buying a new number, it **must** support both inbound calls and Local "
"CLI."
msgstr ""
"Saat membeli nomor baru, nomor tersebut **harus** mendukung panggilan masuk "
"dan Local CLI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:None
msgid "The purchase dashboard in DIDWW."
msgstr "Dashboard pembelian di DIDWW."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:33
msgid "Enable phone.systems"
msgstr "Aktifkan phone.systems"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:35
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Cloud Phone System` in the dashboard sidebar. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Launch admin UI`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Cloud Phone System` di bilah sisi dashboard. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Launch admin UI`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:39
msgid ""
"The *phone.systems PBX* feature is an extra paid service in DIDWW, and may "
"require additional fees."
msgstr ""
"Fitur *phone.systems PBX* adalah layanan berbayar tambahan di DIDWW, dan "
"mungkin memerlukan biaya tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:42
msgid ""
"To create a new user, click :guilabel:`Users`, click the plus sign, then "
"enter the necessary information."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat user baru, klik :guilabel:`Users`, klik tanda plus, kemudian "
"masukkan informasi yang diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:None
msgid "The add a new user screen in DIDWW."
msgstr "Layar tambah user baru di DIDWW."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:48
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Contact Methods`, then click the plus sign to add a new "
"*SIP Device Route*."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Contact Methods`, kemudian klik tanda plus untuk menambahkan "
"*SIP Device Route* baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:50
msgid "Configure or add the following parameters:"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan atau tambahkan parameter berikut:"

