msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allowed Codecs`: `OPUS`, `PCMU`, `PCMA`, `telephone-event`, "
"`g722`, `g729`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Codec yang Diizinkan`: `OPUS`, `PCMU`, `PCMA`, `telephone-event`, "
"`g722`, `g729`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:53
