msgid "Odoo user setting"
msgstr "Pengaturan user Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/onsip.rst:79
msgid ""
"Next, the user needs to be set up in Odoo. Every user associated with an "
"OnSIP user **must** also be configured in the Odoo user's settings/"
"preferences."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, user perlu diatur di Odoo. Setiap user yang terkait dengan user "
